    "These frameworks, multimodal and data-aware, focus on responsive and interactive emergency response.",
    "In the following sections, we elaborate on the technical specifications of the proposed systems, offer comparisons with various open-source models, address the challenges faced, and evaluate the potential of AI-driven solutions in managing emergencies within complex urban settings.II.",
    "ENHANCING 911 DISPATCH EFFICIENCY WITH LLM INTEGRATION The proposed framework integrates Large Language Models (LLMs) into critical communication systems, specifically tailoring this integration to enhance the 911 dispatch process.",
    "Central to this system is the real-time processing and analysis of emergency calls using LLMs, which operate alongside human dispatchers to improve response efficiency.",
